===Etymology===
{{etyl|fr}} {{term|accident|lang=fr}}, from Latin {{term|accidens}}, {{term||-dentis}}, present participle of {{term|accido||to happen|lang=la}}; {{term|lang=la|ad}} + {{term|cadere||to fall|lang=la}}. See {{term|cadence}}, {{term|case}}.

===Pronunciation===
